column6: SWIFT AND TERRIBLE PART 1 Having finally seen his face, Wolverine sets out to rescue his son from the grasp of the shadow society that once enslaved him. But Logan's son doesn't want to be rescued, he wants vengeance!
column8: | penciller:Steve Dillon | letterer:Randy Gentile | colorist:Dan Kemp | penciller (cover):Joe Quesada | writer:Daniel Way
